@CoyoteSings Your symptoms are suggestive of #narcolepsy. These are the 4 classic symptoms, but only 25% have all of them.
@CoyoteSings There are many causes of daytime fatigue, so it's worth seeing a sleep doctor. However, the leg collapse suggest #narcolepsy.
@CoyoteSings Cataplexy is the hallmark of #narcolepsy, but can also be caused by stroke or brain injury. Did your leg collapse start then?
@CoyoteSings Also, brain injury and stroke can trigger #narcolepsy in genetically susceptible people.
